# Expense Operating Staff Training Services Amount

## identifier
de7565

## type
float

## definition
This is the value of expenses recognised in relation to payments to consultants, institutions or other businesses for the provision of staff training and education services.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=debit
- name=Expense.Operating.StaffTrainingServices.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpr/bafpr2.02.06
- period=duration
